              "content": "=I want you to customixe email based on the provided info. just write the email contends so dont specify anything. \n\nfirst name : {{ $json['First Name : '] }}\nlast name : {{ $json['Last Name : '] }}\ne-mail : {{ $json['E-mail : '] }}\nphone number : {{ $json['Phone Number :'] }}\nwork description : {{ $json['Work Description : '] }}\nsite type : {{ $json['Site Type :'] }}\ntimeline : {{ $json['Timeline : '] }}\n\n\n\nE-mail template:\n\nHello (First name)\n\nHow are you? I just received your onboarding form's data. It seems you want use to make you (paraphrased Work description). You're preferring the site to be (side type) and within (timeline).\n\nCould you please confirm your phone number (Phone Number) one last time?\n\nThanks\nNSS\n"
            }
