            },
            {
              "content": "=Candidate Data:\n- First Name: {{ $json['First Name'] }}\n- Last Name: {{ $json['Last Name'] }}\n- Title: {{ $json['Title'] }}\n- Company: {{ $json['Company Name'] }}\n- Summary: {{ $json['Summary'] }}\n- Description: {{ $json['Description on LinkedIn profile'] }}\n\nBased on the candidate data. i want you to generate Subject, Icebreaker, ElevatorPitch, CallToAction and Postscript. \n\nhere are the remplate i want you to follow:\n\nSubject : \"Hey {name} think i have something for you re: {UniquethingAboutThemOrTheCompany}\"\n\nIcebreaker : \"I know you are working on {thing} and I've been following {similarThings} for a while. So i figure having chat make sence.\"\n\nElevatorPitch : \"i think i can add ~5k/mon to {theirBusiness} with few automated systems\"\n\nCallToAction : \"I just did this for a very similar {industry} company and we hit $28,520 in few months they do {relatedThings} so I am very confident I can duplicage this a minimum. Would be 100% risk free and I'd gaurantee at least 20 ppts or you pay nothing. \"\n\nPpstscript : even though we just chat I'd love to hear what your doing with {things}\n\n"
            }
          ]
        },
